\h Malakai 
\toc3 MAL 
\toc2 Malakai 
\toc1 God…®n Akam Inigha Izir Gumazim Malakain Ak…®nafarim 
\mt1 God…®n Akam Inigha Izir Gumazim // Malakain Ak…®nafarim 
\mt2 O 
\mt1 Malakai 
\imt1 Akar faragha zuim 
\ip God…®n akaba inigha ziar gumazim Malakai, a God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir igharazibar g…®n, a uan akam akuri. Dughiar kam…®n Judaba Jerusalem…®n God…®n D…®penim…®n ingarigha g…®fa. God…®n D…®penim g…®vaz…®, Malakai garima, God…®n ziam fer arazir maba ko, ofabagh amir arazir maba mong derazir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a ofa gamir gumaziba ko, gumazamiziba gavgavim men n…®ghn…®zibar an…®ngasa akam akuri, eght…® me deraghv…®ra God…®n damazim…®n arazir aghuibar g…®n mangam. 
\ip Malakai God…®n Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavibagh n…®ghn…®gha akar av…®ribav gei. An Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir kam…®n apengan ikiasa Judabav gei. Gumaziba deraghv…®ra uan amuibar porogh ik…®, egh me arazir aghuibar amuamin gumazamizibar otivam. 
\ip Malakai arazir kuraba ko, navim giraghamin arazim…®n gun m…®gei. Egha a uaghan Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n dughiar otivamim…®n gun m…®gei, eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God gumazamiziba bar men araziba tuis…®gham. 
\ip Malakain akar abuananam m…®g…®a ghaze, Elaija izeght…® an g…®n, God amizir akar d…®k…®r…®zim…®n g…®n mang…®va bizir aghuir av…®ribar amuam. Akar aghuir kam, a God…®n akam inigha izir gumazibar ak…®nafariba ag…®fa, egha en n…®ghn…®zibagh ekuigha, God uan gumazamiziba ko, damuamin Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir Igiam bagha zui. Ez…® akar aghuir kam…®n m…®ngarim, ensel Gebriel ofa gamir gumazim Sekaraia m…®g…®a ghaze, a Gumazamiziba Ruer Gumazim Jon…®n afeziam…®n otogham. Ensel ghaze, Jon God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Malakain akabar amight…® da guizbang…®ra otivam. N…® Luk 1:15-17…®n gan. 
\c 1  
\ms1 E Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n apengan ik…®, egh bizir e amiba bagh  // ziar ekiam a dan…®ngam 
\mr (Sapta 1--4) 
\s1 God bar Israelia gifonge 
\p  
\v 1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelia m…®k…®masa akar kam isa Malakai gan…®ngi.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 1:2 \xt Jenesis 25:21-26\x*\x - \xo 1:2-3 \xt Rom 9:13\x*\x - \xo 1:2-5 \xt Aisaia 34:5-17; 63:1-6; Jeremaia 49:7-22; Esekiel 25:12-14; 35:1-15; Amos 1:11-12; Obadia 1:1-14\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n m…®gei, вАЬK…® bar fom…®ra ia gifueghav…®ra iti.вАЭ Ez…® ia ghaze, вАЬN…® manmagh…®ram e gifonge?вАЭ 
\p Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God ghaze, вАЬIa oragh, fom…®ra Jekop ko Iso, aning aveghbuamning, ez…® k…® Jekop gifuegha, Ison aghua.  
\v 3 Iso uan ovavir boriba ko, me Idomia me gar…®si, ez…® k…® me gifongezir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® Ison danganir m…®ghs…®am gas…®ghasigha g…®fa, egha an nguazim gamiz…®ma, an afiar atiabar nguibam…®n oto.вАЭ 
\p  
\v 4 Eght…® Idomia kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, вАЬEn nguibar ekiaba ikuvigha g…®fa, ez…® e uam adar ingaram,вАЭ eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim men akam ikaragh m…®k…®m suam, вАЬIa uam adar ingart…®, k…® da ap…®raright…® da ua bar ikuvigham. Eght…® gumazamizir igharaziba, me Idomia ia m…®k…®m suam, вАШMe gumazamizir kuraba,вАЩ egha вАШMe gumazamizir, Ikiav…®ra Itir God zuraram atariba.вАЩвАЙвАЭ  
\v 5 Ia Israelian gumazamiziba, ia uan damazibar bizir kam…®n ganam. Egh ia kamagh m…®k…®m suam, вАЬIkiav…®ra Itir God, gavgavir ekiam ikia, Israelia iararam akurvazir puvat…®, a uaghan kantrin igharazibar ingangarir gavgavibagh ami.вАЭ 
\s1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God  // ofa gamir gumazibar atari 
\p  
\v 6 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim kamagh…®n ofa gamir gumazibav g…®a ghaze, вАЬBoriba uan afeziabar apengan ikia men ziaba fe, ez…® ingangarir gumaziba uan gumazir dapanibar apengan ikia men akabar g…®n zui. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia oragh. K…® ian afeziam. Ia manmagh…®n amigha nan apengan itir puvat…®? K…® ian gumazir dapanim. Ia manmagh…®ra amigha nan akabar g…®n zuir puvat…®? Ia nan aghuagha ak…®rim ragha na gasi. Egha ia kamagh…®n na m…®g…®a ghaze, вАШE manmagh…®ra n…®n aghuagha ak…®rim ragha n…® gasi?вАЩ  
\v 7 Ia oraght…®, k…® ian arazir kuram…®n gun ia m…®k…®mam. Ia nan ofabagh amir dakozim…®n as…®zir kuraba inigha iza ofaba tue. Egha ia g…®n kamagh…®n nan azangs…®si, вАШE manmagh…®ra n…®n ziam gas…®ghas…®ki?вАЩ K…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ia m…®k…®mam. Ia ghaze, nan ofa gamir dakozim ti pura bizim, ia kamagh…®n amua nan ziam gas…®ghas…®ki.  
\v 8 Ia ofa gamua, as…®zir damazir okav…®r…®zir mam inigha na bagha an ofa gami, ia ghaze, ian arazir kam ti deras, o? Egha ia as…®zir ar…®mariaba itiba ko, agharir d…®b…®riba, ia da isa na bagha ofa damuasa da inigha izi, ia amir arazir kam a deras, o? Ia as…®zir kamagh garitam is…® uan gavman…®n faragha zuir gumazir dapanim danight…®, a ti ia amizir arazir kam gifuegham, o? Egh a bizir kam ikarvagh bizir bar aghuitam ia dan…®ngam, o? Ti bar puvat…®gham! K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, k…® kamagh…®n ia m…®keme.вАЭ\f + \fr 1:8 \ft N…® God…®n Araziba 15:21…®n itir akam…®n ganigh.\f* 
\p  
\v 9 Aria, ia ofa gamir gumaziba, ia God deragh e damus…® an azangs…®gh. Eght…® a bar ian azangs…®zim bareghan koght…®, tinara os…®mt…®zir kam ateram? Os…®mt…®zir kam iarara aneteram. Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, kamagh…®n ia m…®gei. 
\p  
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt Aisaia 1:11; Jeremaia 6:20; Amos 5:21\x*Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim ghaze, вАЬKamagh…®n ti deragham, gumazitam nan D…®penim…®n tiar akaba asegham, eght…® gumazitam aven mang…® ofan m…®ngariba puvat…®zir kabar amus…® ofa gamir dakozim…®n avim ar…®ghan kogham. K…® ian arazir kabagh ifongezir puvat…®. Egh ofan ia na bagha inigha iziba, k…® da inian kogham. 
\p  
\v 11 вАЬK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, k…® ghaze, gumazamizir aruem anadi nagh…®n itiba ko, aruem uaghiri nagh…®n itir kantriba, me bar mogh…®ra ziar ekiam na gan…®di. Nguibaba bar dar gumazamiziba mughuriar aghuim zuir ofaba ko, ofan igharazir guar av…®riba sara na dan…®ngam. Gumazamizir kaba me bar mogh…®ra ziar ekiam na gan…®di.  
\v 12 Ez…® ia nan ofa gamir dakozim m…®g…®a ghaze, a pura bizim, egha dagher kurar ia aghuaziba, ia da isa ofan m…®n na gan…®di. Ia kamagh…®n amua nan ziam fer puvat…®.\f + \fr 1:12 \ft Hibrun akam deragha akar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f* 
\v 13 Ia kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, вАШOio, e ofa damuamin arazim a bar e baseme.вАЩ Ez…® ian arazir kam kamagh…®n akagha ghaze, ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim…®n ziar ekiam, a gan…®dir puvat…®. Ia as…®zir atiaba m…®soghezir as…®ziba isa, dar ofabagh ami. Ia uaghan as…®zir ar…®mariaba itiba ko, agharir d…®b…®riba isa na bagha izi. Egha ia ghaze, K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® ti ia amir ofan kabagh ifuegham, a? Ti bar puvat…®gham!  
\v 14 Ian tina, na ko ofa damuasa akam ak…®righa inabazir as…®zir m…®karziba sara itir aghuiba ategha, as…®zir kurar m…®z…®r…®ziba inigha Ikiav…®ra Itir God, bagha izi. Ia ifavarir arazir kam bang…®n ia ivezir kuram iniam. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim. K…® atrivibar Ekiam, ez…® kantribar gumazamiziba bar nan atiatia nan ziamra fe. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® bizir kam bagh ia gas…®ghasigham.вАЭ 
\c 2  
\p  
\v 1 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n m…®gei, вАЬO, ofa gamir gumaziba, k…® Akar Gavgavir mam ia m…®k…®masa.  
\v 2 Ia na bagh ingangaribar amus…®, ia guizbang…®ra nan ziar ekiam famin ingangaribar amu. Ia nan akaba batogh da baraghan koght…®, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, k…® kamagh…®n m…®gei, ia bar ikuvigham. Egh bizir aghuir ia uarir akurvaghasa isiba, k…® dagh as…®ghasigham. Ia ghaze, k…® ti pura m…®gei, egha nan akaba batosi. Kamagh…®n, k…® ia gas…®ghasigha g…®fa.  
\v 3 Ia oragh, ia bang…®n k…® ian ovavir boriba ivezir kuram me dan…®ngam. Egh ia ofa gamir as…®zibar buariba is…® ian guabar aghuigham. Egh ia batueght…®, ia mang…® me as…®zibar buariba akuri nagh…®n ikiam.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 2:4 \xt D…®boboniba 3:11-13\x*K…® kamagh…®n damight…®, ia ganigh fogh suam, k…® uab…® Akar Gavgavir kam isa ia gan…®ngi. Ia ofa gamir gumaziba, ia Livain ovavir boriba, Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir k…® ian adarazi ko amizir kam, ia aneb…®ghan mark…®. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, k…® m…®kemegha g…®fa. 
\p  
\v 5 \x - \xo 2:5 \xt D…®boboniba 25:12\x*вАЬNan Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir kam, k…® me ko akam ak…®righa ghaze, ofa gamir gumaziba me dughiar ruarim…®n nguazim…®n ik…®t…®, k…® dabirabir aghuim me dan…®ngam. K…® kamagh…®n me damight…®ma, me nan ziam fam. Me faragha nan apengan ikia, nan ziam fes.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 2:6 \xt God…®n Araziba 33:10; Jeremaia 23:22; Jems 5:20\x*Me guiz…®n arazibar gumazamizibar sure gami. Egha arazir kuratam…®n men sure gamizir puvat…®. Ez…® men ik…®r…®m…®rim na ko bar dera. Egha me uari arazir aghuibaram amua gumazamizir igharazir av…®ribar akurvazima, me arazir kuraba atagh…®rasi.  
\v 7 Kar ofa gamir gumazibar ingangarim, me gumazamizibar sure damut…®, me guizbang…®ra na g…®fogham. Ofa gamir gumaziba, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim…®n akam akurir gumaziba. 
\p  
\v 8 вАЬK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, k…® kamagh…®n ia m…®g…®a ghaze, Ia ofa gamir gumaziba, ia dat…®r…®gh…®n guiz…®n nan tuavim ataki. Ian suren ifavariba gumazamizibagh amiz…®, me iregha arazir kurar mabagh amigha g…®fa. Bar guizbang…®ra, ia Livain adarasi, k…® ia ko amizir Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim, ia anebigha g…®fa.  
\v 9 Ia nan akabar g…®n zuir puvat…®. Egha gumazamizibar sure damuasa akar magh garibar men sure gamir puvat…®. Ia marazi akar is…®ngt…®zibar me m…®g…®a egha marazir atari. Kamagh…®n, k…® Israelia damight…® me ak…®riba ia gasegh ian aghuagham.вАЭ 
\s1 Israelia God ataki 
\p  
\v 10 E bar mogh…®ra afeziar vam…®ra iti. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n vam…®ra an e gamiz…® e otifi. Egha manmaghsuav…®ra, e uari uan namakaba ko, d…®k…®r…®zir akaba ab…®aghar…®si? Egha manmaghsuav…®ra, e Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en ovaviba ko D…®k…®r…®zir Akar Gavgavim an g…®n zuir puvat…®? Arazir kam, bar ikufi! 
\p  
\v 11 Fom…®ra Israelia ko Judaba, me God…®n akam…®n g…®n mangasa akar mam ak…®ri. Ez…® puvat…®, me anebigha uam arazir bar kurar mam gami. Arazir kurar kam me kantrin aven nguibabar bar a gamua, egha uaghan Jerusalem…®n a gami. Men gumazir maba, asebar ziaba fer adarazir amiziba isa dar iti. Ez…® men arazir kam, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penir a bar ifongezim gamiz…®, a bar an damazim…®n m…®ze.  
\v 12 K…® kamaghsua, Ikiav…®ra Itir God gumazir kamagh amiba bar me ag…®vaght…®, me ko men ik…®ziba sara ua Israelian gumazamizibar tong…®n ikian kogham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, men tav ua Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim bagh ofaba inigh mangan kogham. 
\p  
\v 13 Ez…® k…® bizir kurar igharazir ia amir mam…®n gun ua ia m…®k…®mam. Ofan ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagha inigha zuiba a ua da isir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, ia pamtem…®n aziava araima, ian temeriba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa gamir dakozim giri.  
\v 14 Ez…® ia kamagh…®n God…®n azangs…®si, вАЬManmagh amiz…®, n…® en ofaba isir puvat…®?вАЭ Bizir kam…®n m…®ngarim kamak…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God fo, n…® fom…®ra uan mugamra ikia, amuim…®n ikiasa God…®n damazim…®n akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavim gamigha ghaze, n…® amizir kam ateghan kogham. Amizim, kar n…®n roroam. Ez…® puvat…®, n…® akar d…®k…®r…®zir kam abigha g…®fa.  
\v 15 Gua poroghamimning, God gua gamiz…®, gua m…®karzir vam…®ra ko, n…®ghn…®zir vam…®ra iti. God tizim bagha arazir kam gami? A kamaghsua, E boriba bat…®t…®, me guizbang…®ra God…®n adarazir ikiam. Egh ia bizir kam bagh deraghv…®ra gan, ia uan amuir inigha itir kaba ko akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavir kaba, ia da ab…®ghan mark…®.\f + \fr 2:15 \ft Hibrun akam deragha akar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f* 
\v 16 God, a Israelian Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, вАЬK…® poroghamiba uari atagh…®razir arazir kam, bar an aghua. N…® uan amuim pazav…®ra a damuam, n…®n arazir kam, mati n…® inim isa gua uaning avaraz…® mogh…®n, n…®n aghums…®zir arazir kuram gua avara, egha mati gua poroghamimning uaning ab…®si. Ia poroghamiba, bar derav…®ra uan ik…®r…®m…®rim geghuv, ifavarir arazibar uari damuan mark…®.вАЭ\f + \fr 2:16 \ft Hibrun akam deragha akar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f* 
\s1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God izamin dughiam rogh…®ra izi 
\p  
\v 17 Ia m…®g…®r…®g…®ar guar av…®ribagh amiz…®ma, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ian m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kaba bar dar am…®ra. Ia kamagh…®n azangs…®si, вАЬE m…®g…®r…®g…®ar manabagh amiz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God en am…®ra?вАЭ Ia kamagh…®n m…®gei, вАЬIkiav…®ra Itir God gumazir arazir kurabagh amibav g…®a ghaze, Me dera, ez…® a me gifonge.вАЭ Egha ia tintinibar kamagh…®n m…®gei, вАЬGumazamiziba ghaze, God arazir aghuibaram amua gumazamizibar araziba ak…®ri. Ez…® e an garima, a guiz…®n arazir katam gamizir puvat…®.вАЭ Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a ian m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kaba bar dar aghua. 
\c 3  
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 3:1 \xt Matyu 11:10; Mak 1:2; Luk 1:76; 7:27\x*Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, a kamagh…®n akam ikaragha ghaze, вАЬIa oragh! K…® uan abuir gumazim amadaght…®ma, a faragh mang…®va na bagh tuavim ak…®ram. Ia ghaze, ia dat…®r…®gh…®n Ekiam bagha gara iti. Eght…® a zuam…®ra iz…® uan D…®penim…®n ikiam. Abuir gumazir ia bar ifongezim iz…®, Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir kam…®n gun ia m…®k…®mam. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, k…® ghaze, An darorim izi.вАЭ  
\v 2 \x - \xo 3:2 \xt Aisaia 33:14; Joel 2:11; Sekaraia 13:9; Matyu 3:10-12; 1 Korin 3:13-15; Akar Mogomem 6:17\x*Eght…® dughiar a izamin kam, tinara an kotiam…®n aven guizbang…®ra m…®k…®mam? Eght…® an azenaram otogh izamin dughiar kam, tinara tugh an ganam? Bar puvat…®gham. Guizbang…®ra, a mati, avim bar puv…®ra isia gol…®n isigha bizir kuraba bar da adangiz…® mogh…®n, a izam. Egh mati, sop…®n gavgavir inir m…®z…®r…®zim rut…® a bar zueghamim…®n m…®n ganam.  
\v 3 Avim gol…®n isima a golrama otivi mogh…®n, a gumazamizibar araziba tuis…®gham. Kamagh…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ingangarir gumazim, Livain adarazir arazir kuraba batuegh, egh Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh ofan aghuiba inigh izam.  
\v 4 Eght…® g…®n Jerusalemia ko, Judaba mati me faragha amiz…® mogh…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh ofan a ifongeziba uam ada inigh izam. Eght…® a da bagh bar akuegham. 
\p  
\v 5 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim ghaze, вАЬK…® iz…® ian araziba tuis…®gham. K…® bar zuam…®ra kot…®n aven gumazamizir kabar arazir kurabar gun me m…®k…®mam. Gumazamizir kabar kara: imezibagh amir gumazamiziba ko, kukunir gumaziba ko, gumazamizir poroghamibagh as…®ghas…®ziba ko, gumazamizir kot…®n akabagh ifariba ko, gumazir dapanir deragha uan ingangarir gumaziba ivezir puvat…®ziba ko, gumazir amizir odiaribagh ifara pura men biziba isiba ko, gumazamizir afeziaba ariaghirezir boribar biziba isiba ko, gumazamizir Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamizir men tong…®n itibar akurvazir puvat…®ziba. Gumazamizir arazir kaba bar dagh amiba me nan apengan itir puvat…®.вАЭ 
\s1 Bizir akuatam God dan…®ngamin arazim…®n akam 
\p  
\v 6 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua ghaze, вАЬK…®rara k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® uan n…®ghn…®zim giraghan kogham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia Jekop…®n ovavir boriba bar g…®vazir puvat…®.  
\v 7 Ian ovaviba fom…®ram amiz…® mogh…®n, ia ami. Ia nan arazir k…® ifongeziba ak…®rim ragha dagh gasaragha dar g…®n zuir puvat…®. Ia uan arazir kuraba ategh ua na bagh iz…®t…®, k…® uan an…®ngagharim ategh ua ia iniam. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, k…® m…®kemegha g…®fa. Ia kamagh…®n m…®gei, вАШE bizir tizim damigh…®va, ua n…® bagh izam?вАЩ  
\v 8 Ez…® k…® ia m…®g…®a ghaze, Ia nan biziba okei. Egha ia ti ghaze, arazir ia amir kam a dera, a? Bar puvat…®. Egha ia arazir kam atagh…®razir puvat…®. Egha ia g…®n ua kamagh…®n nan azangs…®si, вАШN…® manmaghsua ghaze e n…®n biziba okei?вАЩ K…® kamagh…®n ia m…®k…®mam, Nan Akar Gavgavim ghaze, ia ingara isir biziba, ia bar da tuiraght…® pozir 10plan otoght…®, ia pozitam is…® na dan…®ngam. Kar nan bizimra.  
\v 9 Guizbang…®ra, k…® pamtem kamagh…®n ia m…®gei, Ia bar mogh…®ra nan biziba okemes. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, ia bar kuram iniam.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 3:10 \xt Ofa Gami 27:30; D…®boboniba 18:21-24; God…®n Araziba 12:6; 14:22-29; 2 Atriviba 7:2; 1 Eghaghaniba 26:20; 2 Eghaghaniba 31:10; Nehemia 10:38; 13:12\x*Ia uan biziba 10plan pozibar arigh egh dar pozir tam inigh iz…® nan d…®penim dat…®gh. Eght…® nan ingangarir gumaziba, dagher av…®riba ikiam. Ia kamagh…®n damight…®, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, k…® uan Nguibam…®n tiar akaba kuigh, uan bizir aghuiba is…® amozim…®n m…®n da ingegham, eght…® ia bizir aghuir av…®rim ik…® egh ua bizitam…®n oteveghan kogham. Ia tuavir kam…®n g…®n mang…® damu ganigh, egh fogh suam, nan akam a bar guizbang…®ra.  
\v 11 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, k…® ghaze, вАШIa kamagh…®n damight…®, k…® apizibar t…®vaght…®, da ian azenibar itir bizibagh as…®ghas…®ghan kogham. Eght…® ian wain…®n aghariba bar puv…®ra b…®t…® dar ov…®ziba ik…® mang…® anizir dughiam…®n otogham.  
\v 12 Eght…® kantrin igharaziba ian ganigh suam, Israelian nguazim bar deraz…®, me deraghav…®ra a gapiagha bar akonge. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, nan akam kamagh…®ra tu.вАЩвАЙвАЭ 
\s1 God ivezir aghuim is…® gumazamizir aghuibar an…®ngam 
\p  
\v 13 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God ghaze, вАЬIa bar akar kurar av…®ribar pamten na m…®gei. Egha ia nan azangs…®gha ghaze, вАШE akar kurar manabara n…® m…®keme?вАЩ  
\v 14 Ia uarira uariv g…®a ghaze, вАШE God…®n ziam fe, ez…® a en akurazir puvat…®. Ez…® e tizim bagh an ziam fam? Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim…®n damazim…®n, e uan arazir kuraba bagha osemegha aziava dar gun a m…®keme, ez…® a bizir aghuitam…®n e gamizir puvat…®. Ez…® e manmaghsua pura uan arazir kurabar gun a m…®keme?  
\v 15 E gumazir uari fa akaba batozibar gari, me bar akuegha deraghav…®ra iti. Ez…® gumazir arazir kurabagh amiba, me bizir aghuir av…®riba iti. Ez…® gumazir arazir kuraba God…®n akakaghasa dagh amiba, me ghaze, God ti me gas…®ghas…®gham, ti puvat…®gham? Ez…® God me gas…®ghas…®ghizir pu. Bar puvat…®.вАЩвАЙвАЭ 
\p  
\v 16 Ez…® g…®n gumazamizir Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n atiatiava an apengan itiba uarira uariv gei, ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God men m…®g…®r…®g…®am barasi. Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®kemez…®, enselba an Nguibam…®n ikia ak…®nafarir r…®ghizir mam isa God…®n damazim…®n an gumazamizir kabar ziaba osiri. Kar gumazamizir Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n atiatiava an apengan ikiava, zurazurara an ziam feba. Ak…®nafarir r…®ghizir kam, kar otivizir biziba g…®n dagh n…®ghn…®ghamin ak…®nafarim.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 3:17 \xt God…®n Araziba 7:6; Onger Akaba 103:13; Taitus 2:14; 1 Pita 2:9\x*Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim ghaze, вАЬGumazamizir kaba, me nan adarazira ikiam. Eght…® dughiar k…® inabazir kam otoght…®, gumazamizir kaba guizbang…®ra na baghv…®ra ikiam. Eght…® nan apangkuvim men ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam, mati borim afeziam…®n ingangarim gamiz…®ma, afeziam an apangkufi.  
\v 18 Eght…® dughiar kam…®n, ia gumazamizir arazir aghuibagh amiba ko arazir kurabagh amiba, k…® me gamir arazim, ia an ganam. Arazir aghuibagh amir gumazim, a nan akam…®n g…®n zui. Ez…® arazir kurabagh amir gumazim, a nan akam batosi.вАЭ 
\c 4  
\s1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Dughiar Ekiam Otivam 
\p  
\v 1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim ghaze, вАЬIa deragh oragh. Dughiatam iz…®t…®, gumazamizir akaba batogha uan ziaba fava arazir kurabagh amiba, avir ekiam tuzibar isi mogh…®n, otogh bar men isit…®, me bar gevegham. Eght…® temer aguatam, o ter bitam ikian kogham.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 4:2 \xt Malakai 3:16; Luk 1:78; Efesus 5:14; 2 Pita 1:19; Akar Mogomem 2:28\x*Eght…® dughiar kam…®n, ia gumazamizir nan ziam fa nan atiatia nan apengan itiba, ia bagh am…®nim tiraght…®, aruem anang ia gisiragh, ian arazir aghuiba akakagham. Mati aruem ia gisiragha gara fefem ian m…®karzibagh an…®di mogh…®n, a ia damut…® ian ar…®mariaba g…®vaght…® ia ghuamaghegham. Egh ia mati bulmakaun nguziba bar akuegha uari akura d…®vazim ategha ivemara azenan zui mogh…®n, ia bar akuegh mang…®.  
\v 3 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar itim ghaze, bizir kabar amuamin dughiam…®n, ia gumazir kurar kaba ia tuzir siribar m…®n me d…®kab…®n me ab…®nigham. 
\p  
\v 4 вАЬK…® Sainain M…®ghs…®am…®n, uan ingarir gumazim Moses gan…®ngizir arazir k…® ifongeziba ko, bizir k…® damuasa ia m…®kemeziba, ia da bak…®n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®. Israelian gumazamiziba bar akar kabar g…®n mangasa, k…® da isa ia gan…®ngi. 
\p  
\v 5 \x - \xo 4:5 \xt Matyu 11:14; 17:10-13; Mak 9:11-13; Luk 1:17; Jon 1:21\x*вАЬNan Dughiar kam, a Dughiar Bar Ekiam, k…® an gumazamizibar amight…® me bar atiatigham. Dughiar kam a t…®ghar otivam, k…® faragh…®v…®ra Elaija amadaght…®ma an akam akurir gumazim…®n m…®n ia bagh izam.  
